  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122490/extras/1240cefe01bce168609951df4428ad31.avif?t=1737737402\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simulator: Parking Lot</strong> is a parking management simulation game. Earn money by upgrading parking spots, expanding the number of spaces, and getting tips by cleaning your customers' cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122490/extras/c7fb04b9ee3cf0eb5d6825bfb77141fe.avif?t=1737737402\" width=800 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Decide which spots to unlock first and how to upgrade them. Be careful with thieves, as they might steal your parking meters and break them.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122490/extras/1240cefe01bce168609951df4428ad31.avif?t=1737737402\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simulator: Parking Lot</strong> is a parking management simulation game. Earn money by upgrading parking spots, expanding the number of spaces, and getting tips by cleaning your customers' cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122490/extras/c7fb04b9ee3cf0eb5d6825bfb77141fe.avif?t=1737737402\" width=800 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Decide which spots to unlock first and how to upgrade them. Be careful with thieves, as they might steal your parking meters and break them.</p>",
